#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"In 2021, we want to focus on improving some of the very core features of "
"Tails, especially for **censorship circumvention**."
msgstr ""
"En el 2021, queremos concentrarnos en mejorar algunas de las funcionalidades "
"centrales de Tails, especialmente en **evadir la censura**."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To support our work in 2021, take a minute now to\n"
"<a href=\"https://tails.boum.org/donate/?r=pt\">donate and fight surveillance and censorship</a>!\n"
msgstr ""
"¡Para apoyar nuestro trabajo en 2021, tómate un minuto ahora para\n"
"<a href=\"https://tails.boum.org/donate/?r=pt\">donar y luchar contra la "
"vigilancia y la censura</a>!\n"

#. type: Title -
#, no-wrap
msgid "Censorship circumvention"
msgstr "Evadir la censura"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We want to completely redesign how to **start Tor and configure Tor "
"bridges**."
msgstr ""
"Queremos rediseñar complemtante cómo **iniciar Tor y configurar puentes de "
"Tor**."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This will make it easier for people in countries where accessing Tor is "
"blocked to circumvent censorship. According to data from the Tor project, "
"the top 5 countries by users of Tor bridges are Russia, Iran, the US, "
"Belarus, and China."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title -
#, no-wrap
msgid "Persistent Storage"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We want to improve the interface of the **Persistent Storage settings**."
msgstr ""
"Queremos mejorar la interface de la **configuración del Almacenamiento "
"Persistente**."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Improving the Persistent Storage was your top priority when we surveyed our "
"users in July. We want to start by improving the usability of its core "
"features and rewriting this 9-year-old Perl application into Python GTK+. "
"This will make it possible to improve it faster in the future."
msgstr ""
"Mejorar el Almacenamiento Persistente era nuestra mayor prioridad cuando "
"encuestamos a los usuarios en julio. Queres empezar por mejorar la "
"usabilidad de sus funcionalidades centrales y reescribiendo está aplicación "
"en Perl de hace 9 años a una en Python GTK+. Esto hará mejorarla más "
"rapidamente en el futuro."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "We also want to make it possible to persist Tor bridges."
msgstr ""
"También queremos hacer posible guardar los puentes de Tor de manera "
"persistente."

#. type: Title -
#, no-wrap
msgid "Security and maintenance"
msgstr "Seguridad y mantenimiento"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"To improve the security of all applications in Tails, we want to **migrate to\n"
"<em>Wayland</em>**. *Wayland* is a new display system for Linux that better\n"
"controls how each application interacts with the rest of the system.\n"
msgstr ""
"Para mejorar la seguridad de todas las aplicaciones en Tails, queremos **"
"migrar a\n"
"<em>Wayland</em>**. *Wayland* es un nuevo sistema de visualización para "
"Linux que controla\n"
"mejor como interactuan las aplicaciones con el resto del sistema.\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"For example, *Wayland* will fix how the [[*Unsafe Browser* can be used to "
"deanonymize you|doc/anonymous_internet/unsafe_browser#security]]."
msgstr ""
"Por ejemplo, *Wayland* corregirá [[la forma en que se puede usar el *"
"Navegador Inseguro* para desanonimizarte|doc/anonymous_internet/"
"unsafe_browser#security]]."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We will also release **Tails 5.0**, based on Debian 11 (Bullseye) at the end "
"of 2021. It will bring new versions of most of the software included in "
"Tails."
msgstr ""

